WEBVTT

00:03:57.050 --> 00:04:00.541
And what connects all the different
tissues in the body

00:04:00.565 --> 00:04:01.715
is blood.

00:04:02.366 --> 00:04:08.191
Blood is the tissue that not only carries
cells that transport oxygen, for example,

00:04:08.215 --> 00:04:09.456
the red blood cells,

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:11.680
or fights infectious diseases,

00:04:11.704 --> 00:04:15.975
but it also carries messenger molecules,

00:04:15.999 --> 00:04:19.911
hormone-like factors
that transport information

00:04:19.935 --> 00:04:24.068
from one cell to another,
from one tissue to another,

00:04:24.092 --> 00:04:25.549
including the brain.

